
								====================================
									  Before Java-8 Date And Time API
								====================================

	-> In java we have 2 class that represent date and time 

		1. java.sql.Date
		2. java.util.Date 

		-> when we perform any date and time related db operation then we use java.sql.Date package classes

		-> when we perform any date and time related application then we use java.util.Date package classes

		-> Before java-8 if we create Date class then here date with time also created 

		-> If we want to time only then we convert them manually using SimpleDateFormat

	java.text.SimpleDateFormat

		-> SimpleDateFormat is predefine class that present in java.text package

		-> These classes are provide the method for Date conversion

		1. Date To String Conversion		=> String format (Date date)
		2. String To Date Conversion		=> Date parse (String str)


